title: Bruce Haack - Farad: The Electric Voice 1970-82 (MP3@320)
description:
"This compilation traces his work from 1970-1982, focusing on his vocoder-heavy tracks. It traces some of Haack's works he did primarily aimed at children, with some of his darker work later, though even some of the kids stuff was pretty dark as the album title 'Electric Lucifer' attests to."
